(177, 1, '2011-11-20 02:08:24', '2011-11-20 02:08:24', '<h3>Description</h3>\r\nFish is the Dish is an initiative of the British government to encourage the comsumption of fish in the UK.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Though Billington Cartmell, the actual contracting company of Cobianzo Co. services, we developed the backend of this website..</span>\r\n\r\nThe maintenance of the website was initially carried out by Billington Cartmell.\r\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\r\nBillington Cartmell provided the designers and front end developers, and Cobianzo Co Ltd developed the backend based on those designs. Once more we worked on Wordpress.\r\n\r\nWe worked on standard Wordpress structures to develop the sections for recipes, news and regular pages.', 'Fish is the Dish backend', 'http://www.fishisthedish.co.uk/', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fish-is-the-dish-backend', '', '', '2014-12-31 02:16:50', '2014-12-31 02:16:50', '', 0, 'SITEURL/?post_type=work&#038;p=177', 0, 'work', '', 0),
