(170, 1, '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '<h3>Description</h3>\nElla''s Kitchen is a leader company in organic baby and toddler food. They sell their products in supermarkets inUK, Norway, Sweden and the United States.\n\nThough Billington Cartmell, the actual contracting company of Cobianzo Co. services, we developed the backend of this website, and other small applications online such as a survey campaign.\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\nBillington Cartmell provided the designers and front end developers, and Cobianzo Co Ltd developed the backend based on those designs. Once more we worked on wordpress.\n\nThe plugin Advanced Custom Fields was a perfect allied for this project, as we have to develop a complex (in its internal structure, not in the way it worked) system to allow the site admin to customize page and colors with wavy edges.', 'Ella''s Kitchen backend', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '167-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '', 167, 'SITEURL/167-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(167, 1, '2014-12-30 23:24:44', '2014-12-30 23:24:44', '<h3>Description</h3>\nElla''s Kitchen is a leader company in organic baby and toddler food. They sell their products in supermarkets inUK, Norway, Sweden and the United States.\n\nThough Billington Cartmell, the actual contracting company of Cobianzo Co. services, we developed the backend of this website, and other small applications online such as a survey campaign.\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\nBillington Cartmell provided the designers and front end developers, and Cobianzo Co Ltd developed the backend based on those designs. Once more we worked on wordpress.\n\nThe plugin Advanced Custom Fields was a perfect allied for this project, as we have to develop a complex (in its internal structure, not in the way it worked) system to allow the site admin to customize page and colors with wavy edges.', 'Ella''s Kitchen backend', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'ellas-kitchen-backend', '', '', '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '2014-12-30 23:32:30', '', 0, 'SITEURL/?p=167', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(168, 1, '2011-12-30 23:22:03', '2011-12-30 23:22:03', '<h3>Description</h3>\r\nElla''s Kitchen is a leader company in <strong>organic baby and toddler food</strong>. They sell their products in supermarkets inUK, Norway, Sweden and the United States.\r\n\r\nThough Billington Cartmell, the actual contracting company of Cobianzo Co. services, we developed the backend of this website, and other small applications online such as a survey campaign.\r\n\r\nThe maintenance of the website was initially carried out by Billington Cartmell.\r\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\r\nBillington Cartmell provided the designers and front end developers, and Cobianzo Co Ltd developed the backend based on those designs. Once more we worked on Wordpress.\r\n\r\nThe plugin Advanced Custom Fields was a perfect allied for this project, as we have to develop a complex (in its internal structure, not in the way it worked) system to allow the site admin to customize page and colors with wavy edges.', 'Ella''s Kitchen backend', 'Ella''s Kitchen is a leader company in organic baby and toddler food. In this project we developed the backend of the British website', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ellas-kitchen-backend', '', '', '2014-12-31 01:52:35', '2014-12-31 01:52:35', '', 0, 'SITEURL/?post_type=work&#038;p=168', 0, 'work', '', 0),
