(152, 1, '2013-07-30 14:12:47', '2013-07-30 14:12:47', '<h3>Description</h3>\r\n<strong>Simplemente Verde</strong> (Simply Green) is an online artificial plants shop. It operates in Spain and Portugal, with base in Murcia. It''s the second biggest seller of artificial plants right after Ikea in Spain.\r\n\r\nThis is the second version of the website that we develop for this client, as the previous one was developed in 2011.\r\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\r\nWe chose Prestashop as the ecommerce framework for this website. We offered the client a set of alternatives for his corporative identity and logo. Then we use an already built solid theme and customized it following the requirements of the client.\r\n\r\nThe website supports three languages, so we hired translators to populate the contents, and worked on the SEO deeoply to give it the highest results in Spanish search in internet.\r\n\r\nFor the previous version of the site we used again Prestashop.', 'Simplemente verde e-commerce', 'Simplemente Verde (Simply Green) is an online artificial plants shop operating in Spain and Portugal.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'simplemente-verde-e-commerce', '', '', '2014-12-30 17:11:58', '2014-12-30 17:11:58', '', 0, 'SITEURL/?post_type=work&#038;p=152', 0, 'work', '', 0),
(153, 1, '2014-12-30 14:53:54', '2014-12-30 14:53:54', '<h3>Description</h3>\n<strong>Simplemente Verde</strong> (Simply Green) is an online artificial plants shop. It operates in Spain and Portugal, with base in Murcia. It''s the second biggest seller of artificial plants right after Ikea in Spain.\n\nThis is the second version of the website that we develop for this client, as the previous one was developed in 2012.\n<h3>Technical Analysis</h3>\nWe chose Prestashop as the ecommerce framework for this website. We offered the client a set of alternatives for his corporative identity and logo. Then we use an already built solid theme and customized it following the requirements of the client.\n\nThe website supports three languages, so we hired translators to\n\nFor the previous version of the site we used again Prestashop.', 'Simplemente verde e-commerce', 'Simplemente Verde (Simply Green) is an online artificial plants shop operating in Spain and Portugal.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '152-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-12-30 14:53:54', '2014-12-30 14:53:54', '', 152, 'SITEURL/152-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
